00:16:28.640 --> 00:16:31.740 align:middle line:84%
>>Merton's journey
to Asia is, I think,

00:16:31.740 --> 00:16:35.772 align:middle line:90%
a culmination of many things.

00:16:35.772 --> 00:16:37.482 align:middle line:90%
He's a seeker.

00:16:37.482 --> 00:16:40.470 align:middle line:90%
He is, in a sense, a pioneer.

00:16:40.470 --> 00:16:42.660 align:middle line:90%
>>He knew so much about it.

00:16:42.660 --> 00:16:43.900 align:middle line:90%
