00:17:23.819 --> 00:17:28.180 align:middle line:84%
starting, that you
don't know anything yet.

00:17:28.180 --> 00:17:33.780 align:middle line:84%
>>And he understood that there's
doctrine, ideology, on the one

00:17:33.780 --> 00:17:37.760 align:middle line:84%
