Merton went to the East,

00:17:59.720 --> 00:18:02.450 align:middle line:84%
as if he'd lost his
Christian faith.

00:18:02.450 --> 00:18:04.970 align:middle line:84%
>>When most of the
Church was saying

00:18:04.970 --> 00:18:09.080 align:middle line:84%
those are no better than
pagans, who are these people

00:18:09.080 --> 00:18:12.230 align:middle line:84%
worshipping, whatever they do,
the Buddha, and all that stuff,

00:18:12.230 --> 00:18:16.120 align:middle line:84%
Merton really saw
that parallel track

00:18:16.120 --> 00:18:19.070 align:middle line:90%
