00:18:19.070 --> 00:18:21.650 align:middle line:84%
>>Merton was this
curious mix of someone

00:18:21.650 --> 00:18:25.210 align:middle line:84%
who could rebel against Church
authority, needle Church

00:18:25.210 --> 00:18:28.080 align:middle line:84%
authority, question
Church authority,

00:18:28.080 --> 00:18:30.780 align:middle line:84%
appreciate and explore
and communicate

00:18:30.780 --> 00:18:35.530 align:middle line:84%
with other religions, and
remain totally Catholic.

00:18:35.530 --> 00:18:37.660 align:middle line:84%
>>It's about seeking
God in kind of things.

00:18:37.660 --> 00:18:41.050 align:middle line:84%
It begins with the intuition
that God is already there

00:18:41.050 --> 00:18:43.870 align:middle line:84%
in the world and
in other persons.

00:18:43.870 --> 00:18:46.950 align:middle line:84%
I mean the alternative for
Merton would be unacceptable.

00:18:46.950 --> 00:18:52.240 align:middle line:84%
That somehow God is not
in other human beings

00:18:52.240 --> 00:18:54.370 align:middle line:90%
in 2/3 of humanity.

00:18:54.370 --> 00:18:57.070 align:middle line:84%
>>At one point, he says,
well, how can I reconcile

00:18:57.070 --> 00:18:59.470 align:middle line:84%
