00:19:23.580 --> 00:19:26.385 align:middle line:84%
share his treasure with the
world through his journals

00:19:26.385 --> 00:19:29.360 align:middle line:90%
and through his writings.

00:19:29.360 --> 00:19:31.935 align:middle line:84%
>>The Zen phrase
