00:19:31.935 --> 00:19:34.310 align:middle line:90%
Well, he had Big Sky Mind.

00:19:34.310 --> 00:19:37.480 align:middle line:90%
He's as open as the sky.

00:19:37.480 --> 00:19:40.945 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:19:40.945 --> 00:20:04.260 align:middle line:90%


00:20:04.260 --> 00:20:08.900 align:middle line:84%
>>On October 14,
1968, Thomas Merton

00:20:08.900 --> 00:20:13.895 align:middle line:84%
