west, to land in the East.

00:20:13.895 --> 00:20:19.010 align:middle line:90%


00:20:19.010 --> 00:20:24.260 align:middle line:10%
>>I'm over a wing and see
only a lovely distant garden

00:20:24.260 --> 00:20:30.530 align:middle line:10%
of delicate Pacific clouds, like
coral, like rich and delicately

00:20:30.530 --> 00:20:34.620 align:middle line:10%
formed, full white
and pink flowers.

00:20:34.620 --> 00:20:38.480 align:middle line:10%
The utter happiness of
life in a plane, quiet,

00:20:38.480 --> 00:20:44.660 align:middle line:10%
time to read, but long,
long, endless noon.

00:20:44.660 --> 00:20:48.380 align:middle line:90%


00:20:48.380 --> 00:20:55.780 align:middle line:84%
Calcutta, smiling, fecal,
detached, tired, inexhaustible,

00:20:55.780 --> 00:20:59.160 align:middle line:84%
young, old, full of young
people who seem old.

00:20:59.160 --> 00:21:02.500 align:middle line:90%
It is the unmasked city.

00:21:02.500 --> 00:21:05.830 align:middle line:84%
It is the subculture of
poverty and overpopulation.

00:21:05.830 --> 00:21:10.580 align:middle line:90%
[LOUD CITY NOISES]

00:21:10.580 --> 00:21:15.240 align:middle line:84%
People, people, people,
campfires in the streets

00:21:15.240 --> 00:21:19.120 align:middle line:84%
and squares; movie posters,
those Asian posters

00:21:19.120 --> 00:21:23.570 align:middle line:84%
with the strange, enormous
faces of violent or demented

00:21:23.570 --> 00:21:25.490 align:middle line:90%
Western gods.

00:21:25.490 --> 00:21:29.460 align:middle line:84%
The enormous gunners surrounded
by impossible writings.

00:21:29.460 --> 00:21:32.300 align:middle line:10%
One has John Wayne
with eight arms.

00:21:32.300 --> 00:21:36.300 align:middle line:84%
Well, he certainly has
enough guns already.

00:21:36.300 --> 00:21:38.465 align:middle line:84%
Or the dance of
Shiva with Sinatra.

00:21:38.465 --> 00:21:41.418 align:middle line:90%


00:21:41.418 --> 00:21:43.870 align:middle line:84%
The situation of
the tourist becomes

00:21:43.870 --> 00:21:47.690 align:middle line:84%
ludicrous and impossible
in a place like Calcutta.

00:21:47.690 --> 00:21:49.940 align:middle line:84%
