00:21:59.530 --> 00:22:01.470 align:middle line:90%
in the best section.

00:22:01.470 --> 00:22:03.205 align:middle line:90%
Yet, the people are beautiful.

00:22:03.205 --> 00:22:05.990 align:middle line:90%


00:22:05.990 --> 00:22:08.990 align:middle line:84%
But the routine of the
beggars is heart-rending.

00:22:08.990 --> 00:22:10.650 align:middle line:84%
The little girl who
suddenly appeared

00:22:10.650 --> 00:22:14.290 align:middle line:84%
