00:23:07.860 --> 00:23:10.776 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:23:10.776 --> 00:23:23.920 align:middle line:90%


00:23:23.920 --> 00:23:28.050 align:middle line:84%
>>Merton attends a conference
