00:24:20.860 --> 00:24:24.680 align:middle line:90%


00:24:24.680 --> 00:24:28.630 align:middle line:84%
>>The curious kid finds
himself interacting

00:24:28.630 --> 00:24:31.810 align:middle line:84%
