00:25:27.760 --> 00:25:34.120 align:middle line:84%
thoughtful, prayerful,
insightful, in-depth.

00:25:34.120 --> 00:25:36.920 align:middle line:10%
But in more informal
remarks, Merton

00:25:36.920 --> 00:25:43.470 align:middle line:10%
