to an establishment.

00:26:16.150 --> 00:26:19.320 align:middle line:84%
He is a marginal person
who withdraws deliberately

00:26:19.320 --> 00:26:22.370 align:middle line:84%
to the margin of society,
with a view of deepening

00:26:22.370 --> 00:26:25.180 align:middle line:90%
fundamental human experience.

00:26:25.180 --> 00:26:28.520 align:middle line:84%
Consequently, as one of
these strange people,

00:26:28.520 --> 00:26:30.300 align:middle line:84%
I speak to you as
a representative

00:26:30.300 --> 00:26:33.230 align:middle line:84%
of all marginal persons who
have done this kind of thing

00:26:33.230 --> 00:26:34.980 align:middle line:90%
deliberately.

00:26:34.980 --> 00:26:37.910 align:middle line:84%
The office of the monk,
or the marginal people,

00:26:37.910 --> 00:26:40.680 align:middle line:84%
or the meditative
person, or the poet,

00:26:40.680 --> 00:26:43.790 align:middle line:84%
is to go beyond death,
even in this life.

00:26:43.790 --> 00:26:46.560 align:middle line:84%
To go beyond the dichotomy
of life and death,

00:26:46.560 --> 00:26:49.440 align:middle line:84%
and therefore be
a witness to life.

00:26:49.440 --> 00:26:51.860 align:middle line:90%
This requires, of course, faith.

00:26:51.860 --> 00:26:53.530 align:middle line:84%
But soon as you
say faith in terms

00:26:53.530 --> 00:26:56.330 align:middle line:84%
of this monastic and
marginal existence,

00:26:56.330 --> 00:26:58.570 align:middle line:90%
you run into another problem.

00:26:58.570 --> 00:27:00.595 align:middle line:90%
Faith means doubt.

00:27:00.595 --> 00:27:02.843 align:middle line:84%
Faith is not the
suppression of doubt.

00:27:02.843 --> 00:27:05.350 align:middle line:90%
It is the overcoming of doubt.

00:27:05.350 --> 00:27:08.270 align:middle line:84%
And you overcome doubt
by going through it.

00:27:08.270 --> 00:27:11.620 align:middle line:84%
A man of faith, who has
never experienced doubt,

00:27:11.620 --> 00:27:13.540 align:middle line:90%
is not a man of faith.

00:27:13.540 --> 00:27:15.720 align:middle line:10%
Consequently, the
monk is one who

00:27:15.720 --> 00:27:18.280 align:middle line:10%
has to struggle in the
depths of his being

00:27:18.280 --> 00:27:20.800 align:middle line:10%
with the presence
of doubt and to go

00:27:20.800 --> 00:27:25.230 align:middle line:10%
through what some religions
call the Great Doubt.

00:27:25.230 --> 00:27:28.780 align:middle line:10%
I stand among you as one who a
offers a small message of hope,

00:27:28.780 --> 00:27:31.240 align:middle line:10%
that first there
are always people

00:27:31.240 --> 00:27:34.720 align:middle line:10%
who dare to seek on the
margin of society, who are not

00:27:34.720 --> 00:27:36.950 align:middle line:10%
dependent on social
acceptance, not

00:27:36.950 --> 00:27:39.410 align:middle line:10%
dependent on social
routines, and prefer

00:27:39.410 --> 00:27:45.090 align:middle line:10%
a kind of free-floating
existence under a state a risk.

00:27:45.090 --> 00:27:47.740 align:middle line:10%
And among these people,
if they are faithful

00:27:47.740 --> 00:27:50.670 align:middle line:10%
to their own calling, and
faithful to their own vocation,

00:27:50.670 --> 00:27:53.480 align:middle line:10%
and faithful to their
own message from God,

00:27:53.480 --> 00:27:57.140 align:middle line:10%
communication on the
deepest level is possible.

00:27:57.140 --> 00:27:59.060 align:middle line:84%
And the deepest level
of communication

00:27:59.060 --> 00:28:02.610 align:middle line:84%
is not communication,
but communion.

00:28:02.610 --> 00:28:03.456 align:middle line:90%
It is wordless.

00:28:03.456 --> 00:28:05.320 align:middle line:90%
It is beyond words.

00:28:05.320 --> 00:28:06.820 align:middle line:90%
And it is beyond speech.

00:28:06.820 --> 00:28:09.585 align:middle line:90%
And it is beyond concept.

00:28:09.585 --> 00:28:11.480 align:middle line:84%
Not that we discover
a new unity.

00:28:11.480 --> 00:28:14.660 align:middle line:90%
We discover an older unity.

00:28:14.660 --> 00:28:18.990 align:middle line:84%
My dear brothers and
sisters, we are already one.

00:28:18.990 --> 00:28:21.050 align:middle line:90%
But we imagine that we are not.

00:28:21.050 --> 00:28:25.010 align:middle line:84%
And what we have to recover
is our original unity.

00:28:25.010 --> 00:28:27.930 align:middle line:84%
What we have to
be is what we are.

00:28:27.930 --> 00:28:31.910 align:middle line:90%


00:28:31.910 --> 00:28:33.340 align:middle line:90%
Oh, God.

00:28:33.340 --> 00:28:35.860 align:middle line:84%
You have taught us that
if we are open to another,

00:28:35.860 --> 00:28:37.732 align:middle line:90%
you dwell in us.

00:28:37.732 --> 00:28:40.430 align:middle line:84%
Let us be bound
together with love

00:28:40.430 --> 00:28:45.020 align:middle line:84%
as we go our diverse ways,
united in this one spirit,

00:28:45.020 --> 00:28:47.530 align:middle line:84%
which makes you
present in the world.

00:28:47.530 --> 00:28:49.310 align:middle line:90%
Love has overcome.

00:28:49.310 --> 00:28:50.700 align:middle line:90%
Love is victorious.

00:28:50.700 --> 00:28:59.960 align:middle line:90%


00:28:59.960 --> 00:29:03.655 align:middle line:90%
>>I'd say amen.

00:29:03.655 --> 00:29:05.010 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, that was a Merton.

00:29:05.010 --> 00:29:06.785 align:middle line:84%
I mean-- and that
was the spirit that

00:29:06.785 --> 00:29:09.886 align:middle line:90%
lay over the entire conference.

00:29:09.886 --> 00:29:14.200 align:middle line:90%
And if only it would happen.

00:29:14.200 --> 00:29:17.215 align:middle line:84%
We did have this sense we're
going to change the world.

00:29:17.215 --> 00:29:20.254 align:middle line:90%


00:29:20.254 --> 00:29:20.920 align:middle line:90%
And I went home.

00:29:20.920 --> 00:29:22.128 align:middle line:90%
The world didn't change much.

00:29:22.128 --> 00:29:23.368 align:middle line:90%
But--you know,

00:29:23.368 --> 00:29:25.932 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC AND SINGING]

00:29:25.932 --> 00:29:42.280 align:middle line:90%


00:29:42.280 --> 00:29:46.370 align:middle line:84%
>>Another young American
named Harold Talbott

00:29:46.370 --> 00:29:51.610 align:middle line:84%
