00:30:03.150 --> 00:30:05.634 align:middle line:84%
He arranges an
audience for Merton.

00:30:05.634 --> 00:30:12.560 align:middle line:90%


00:30:12.560 --> 00:30:15.030 align:middle line:10%
>>I was living in a bungalow.

00:30:15.030 --> 00:30:17.680 align:middle line:10%
And I gave my room
and study to Merton.

00:30:17.680 --> 00:30:22.650 align:middle line:84%
