00:30:39.686 --> 00:30:40.310 align:middle line:90%
in the morning.

00:30:40.310 --> 00:30:45.490 align:middle line:90%


00:30:45.490 --> 00:30:47.780 align:middle line:84%
>>I am not exactly
dizzy with the idea

00:30:47.780 --> 00:30:49.680 align:middle line:90%
