00:32:30.980 --> 00:32:32.710 align:middle line:90%
He was on a roll.

00:32:32.710 --> 00:32:36.190 align:middle line:84%
He was on a toot, on
a holiday from school.

00:32:36.190 --> 00:32:40.090 align:middle line:10%
He was the grand
senor, the great lord

00:32:40.090 --> 00:32:41.365 align:middle line:10%
of the spiritual life.

00:32:41.365 --> 00:32:47.000 align:middle line:90%


00:32:47.000 --> 00:32:48.730 align:middle line:84%
>>The first meeting
with His Holiness

00:32:48.730 --> 00:32:51.970 align:middle line:84%
