00:33:19.150 --> 00:33:21.980 align:middle line:90%
by saying, what do you want?

00:33:21.980 --> 00:33:58.872 align:middle line:90%


00:33:58.872 --> 00:33:59.610 align:middle line:10%
[CHANTING]

00:33:59.610 --> 00:34:00.110 align:middle line:90%


00:34:00.110 --> 00:34:03.640 align:middle line:84%
>>The Dalai Lama is most
impressive as a person.

00:34:03.640 --> 00:34:06.392 align:middle line:84%
