[BELL CHIMING]

00:37:46.210 --> 00:37:46.710 align:middle line:90%


00:37:46.710 --> 00:37:50.480 align:middle line:84%
>>Merton had a highly
playful manner.

00:37:50.480 --> 00:37:52.520 align:middle line:84%
He was lots of fun
