00:38:29.430 --> 00:38:34.300 align:middle line:84%
And that was the basis on
which he was met by everybody

00:38:34.300 --> 00:38:38.020 align:middle line:84%
and congratulated valiantly,
whether they recognized

00:38:38.020 --> 00:38:40.930 align:middle line:90%
his public identity or not.

00:38:40.930 --> 00:38:44.410 align:middle line:84%
People knew his
spiritual quality.

00:38:44.410 --> 00:38:46.680 align:middle line:90%
People in Plains knew it.

00:38:46.680 --> 00:38:48.450 align:middle line:90%
There was no question about it.

00:38:48.450 --> 00:38:52.630 align:middle line:84%
Merton was not an object of
scrutiny, he was an event.

00:38:52.630 --> 00:38:59.590 align:middle line:90%


00:38:59.590 --> 00:39:05.610 align:middle line:84%
>>As Merton travels, he is
writing, always writing.

00:39:05.610 --> 00:39:10.270 align:middle line:84%
