some simply observations

00:39:10.270 --> 00:39:11.457 align:middle line:90%
of a journey.

00:39:11.457 --> 00:39:14.140 align:middle line:90%


00:39:14.140 --> 00:39:19.140 align:middle line:84%
>>Down in the valley, a
bird sings, a boy whistles,

00:39:19.140 --> 00:39:22.240 align:middle line:84%
