00:40:10.216 --> 00:40:13.060 align:middle line:90%


00:40:13.060 --> 00:40:14.790 align:middle line:90%
The sun in Calcutta.

00:40:14.790 --> 00:40:16.160 align:middle line:90%
Are you worried?

00:40:16.160 --> 00:40:17.786 align:middle line:90%
Refresh yourself with cigars.

00:40:17.786 --> 00:40:22.090 align:middle line:90%


